{{main|Steven Stone (anime)}}
Steven Stone is a recurring character in {{aniseries|PTS}} and {{aniseries|HZ}}. He debuted in a minor role in the {{aniseries|RS}} episode ''[[AG022|A Hole Lotta Trouble]]'', before reappearing as a {{pkmn|Champion}} and an ally to [[Alain]] in the ''[[Mega Evolution Specials]]'' with a {{shiny}} {{TP|Steven|Metagross}}. He later assisted {{ash}} and {{ashfr}} during the climax of the [[Team Flare]] arc during {{aniseries|XY}}, and took part in the [[Masters Eight Tournament]] in {{aniseries|JN}}.
